name: Dapphack
body:
### General info.
Because it's fun to hack together we plan to create a hackathon weekend in Berlin for [EtherCamp](hack.ether.camp)

### Dates
11-13 Nov, 2016

### Location
We are planning to be in a to the subject relevant office in Berlin
